author: DAN ALBANO
title: Inside O.C. Water Polo Podcast: CdM; Wednesday's showdowns (Part 1)
text:
Download this MP3 Share this on Facebook or Twitter Released: October 13, 2015 By: Dan Albano @ocvarsityguy 
Matt Szabo of The Daily Pilot joins Dan Albano of The Orange County Register and Coach Steve Carrera of Orange Lutheran to discuss Corona del Mar's boys water polo team after the the S & R Sport tourney and preview Wednesday's showdowns: Newport Harbor-Huntington Beach and Mater Dei-Harvard-Westlake. This is Part 1 of a podcast that covers the transfers and the public vs. private debate in Part 2. Dan Albano's podcasts on high school football and water polo 
Orange County Register high school sports reporter Dan Albano (@ocvarsityguy) talks Trinity League football with Scott Barajas, former publish of Gridiron magazine, and water polo with Coach Steve Carrera of Orange Lutheran and Northwood Water Polo Club (@stevecarrera). Listen for the inside scoop! Trinity League Football Podcast (Episode 7): Round 1 previews October 8, 2015 Dan Albano of The Orange County Register and OCVarsity.com and Scott Barajas, former publisher of Gridiron magazine, preview the opening round of the Trinity League. Inside O.C. Water Polo Podcast: Previews of league showdowns, transfers, S & R Sport October 6, 2015 Dan Albano of OCVarsity.com and The Orange County Register joins Coach Steve Carrera of Orange Lutheran to preview the start of play in the Sunset and Trinity League, impact transfers from the sitout period and this weekend's S & R Sport Cup in Irvine. Trinity League Podcast Episode 6: Rankings, grades going into league October 1, 2015 Dan Albano of OCVarsity.com and The Orange County Register and Scott Barajas, former publisher of Gridiron magazine, stay sharp in the Trinity League bye week by ranking positions and unit based on nonleague performance and grading each team going into league play Oct. 9. Inside O.C. Water Polo Podcast: Rankings shaken after South Coast Tournament September 30, 2015 Dan Albano of OCVarsity.com and The Orange County Register talks about the O.C. water polo scene with Orange Lutheran coach Steve Carrera. Trinity League Football Podcast Episode 5: What happened to Santa Margarita and Pac-5 preview September 24, 2015 Dan Albano of OCVarsity.com and The Orange County Register joins Scott Barajas to breakdown the latest news in the Trinity League and take a first look at the Pac-5 Division.
